Entrepreneur - November 2013  IN

116 Pages | True PDF | English | 10 MB


Entrepreneur INDIA is the indispensable handbook for both aspiring and existing entrepreneurs in starting and expanding their businesses. It contains sound business advice from experts and essential know-how aimed at giving each reader the edge to succeed in business. It also provides motivational guidance and inspirational features that give readers a framework for entrepreneurial success, helping readers become their own boss and turn their business ideas into reality.
